Auto Quote OmniScript

The Auto Quote OmniScript is called by two other OmniScripts, ReusableDriverInput and ReusableVehicleInput. It calls these scripts to create a quote. The process flow for the Auto Quote OmniScript looks like this.

It's built using LWCs (Lightning Web Components) that can be learned about in Insurance Lightning Web Component UI Development Kit.
